reviewText: Modern day quality is better. Songs are great and make up for video shot over 13-15 years ago. Good old country!

You get the following videos:

1. All my Rowdy Friends are coming over tonight
2. there's a tear in my beer with Hank Sr.
3. Everything comes down to Money & Love
4. Come on over to the Country
5. My Name is Bocephus
6. Young Country
